ents of triumph. However, we recognise that our work is far from over. We must remain vigilant in the fight against discrimination, injustice, and prejudice in all its forms.</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-egiyK kKHsVi pf-275_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-ilfuhL ejXpQB pf-276_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-dtMgUX gYEGeC pf-277_ pf-heading-1-h3">How you can get involved</h3><p class="sc-cZMNgc hqfPHB pf-279_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">There are countless ways to get involved and show your support during Pride Month and beyond:</p><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-bQtKYq czWvgn pf-281_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fXEqDS gMGtOR pf-282_ pf-text-1">Participate in Pride events and celebrations in your community.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fXEqDS gMGtOR pf-284_ pf-text-1">Educate yourself about LGBTQ+ issues and history.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fXEqDS gMGtOR pf-286_ pf-text-1">Support LGBTQ+ organisations and initiatives through donations or volunteering.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fXEqDS gMGtOR pf-288_ pf-text-1">Advocate for LGBTQ+ rights and equality in your workplace, school, and community.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fXEqDS gMGtOR pf-290_ pf-text-1">Be an ally to LGBTQ+ friends, family members, and colleagues by offering support and understanding.</li></ul></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-ilfuhL ejXpQB pf-292_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/young-woman-wearing-gay-pride-mask-and-rainbow-fla-2023-11-27-05-21-44-utc.jp